## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="437bb-103">将 `AutoResetEvent` 、 <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent> 和 <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> 用于线程交互 (或线程信号) 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-103">You use `AutoResetEvent`, <xref:System.Threading.ManualResetEvent>, and <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> for thread interaction (or thread signaling).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-104">有关详细信息，请参阅[同步基元概述](/dotnet/standard/threading/overview-of-synchronization-primitives)一文中的 "[线程交互" 或 "信号](/dotnet/standard/threading/overview-of-synchronization-primitives#thread-interaction-or-signaling)" 部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-104">For more information, see the [Thread interaction, or signaling](/dotnet/standard/threading/overview-of-synchronization-primitives#thread-interaction-or-signaling) section of the [Overview of synchronization primitives](/dotnet/standard/threading/overview-of-synchronization-primitives) article.</span></span>  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="437bb-105">此类型实现 <xref:System.IDisposable> 接口。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-105">This type implements the <xref:System.IDisposable> interface.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-106">在使用完类型后，您应直接或间接释放类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-106">When you have finished using the type, you should dispose of it either directly or indirectly.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-107">若要直接释放类型，请在 `try`/`catch` 块中调用其 <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A> 方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-107">To dispose of the type directly, call its <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A> method in a `try`/`catch` block.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-108">若要间接释放类型，请使用 `using`（在 C# 中）或 `Using`（在 Visual Basic 中）等语言构造。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-108">To dispose of it indirectly, use a language construct such as `using` (in C#) or `Using` (in Visual Basic).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-109">有关详细信息，请参阅 <xref:System.IDisposable> 接口主题中的“使用实现 IDisposable 的对象”一节。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-109">For more information, see the "Using an Object that Implements IDisposable" section in the <xref:System.IDisposable> interface topic.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="437bb-110">线程通过调用 AutoResetEvent 等待信号[。](xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-110">A thread waits for a signal by calling [AutoResetEvent.WaitOne](xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-111">如果 `AutoResetEvent` 处于非终止状态，则线程将会阻塞，直到调用 [AutoResetEvent](xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A) 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-111">If the `AutoResetEvent` is in the non-signaled state, the thread blocks until [AutoResetEvent.Set](xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A) is called.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="437bb-112">调用 `Set` 信号 `AutoResetEvent` 以释放等待线程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-112">Calling `Set` signals `AutoResetEvent` to release a waiting thread.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-113">`AutoResetEvent` 在一个等待线程释放之前保持终止状态，然后自动返回到非终止状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-113">`AutoResetEvent` remains signaled until a single waiting thread is released, and then automatically returns to the non-signaled state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-114">如果没有等待的线程，状态将保持无限期通知。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-114">If no threads are waiting, the state remains signaled indefinitely.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="437bb-115">如果线程 <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A> <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> 在处于终止状态时调用，则线程不会阻塞。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-115">If a thread calls <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitOne%2A> while the <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> is in the signaled state, the thread does not block.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-116"><xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent>立即释放该线程并返回到非终止状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-116">The <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> releases the thread immediately and returns to the non-signaled state.</span></span>  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="437bb-117">不保证每次调用 <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A> 方法都将释放一个线程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-117">There is no guarantee that every call to the <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A> method will release a thread.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-118">如果两次调用都过于接近，因此在释放线程之前发生第二次调用，则只释放一个线程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-118">If two calls are too close together, so that the second call occurs before a thread has been released, only one thread is released.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-119">这就像第二次调用没有发生。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-119">It's as if the second call did not happen.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-120">此外，如果在没有 <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A> 等待的线程并且已 <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> 发出信号的情况下调用，则调用不起作用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-120">Also, if <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A> is called when there are no threads waiting and the <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> is already signaled, the call has no effect.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="437bb-121">可以 `AutoResetEvent` 通过将布尔值传递到构造函数来控制的初始状态： `true` 如果初始状态为 "已终止"，则为 `false` ; 否则为。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-121">You can control the initial state of an `AutoResetEvent` by passing a Boolean value to the constructor: `true` if the initial state is signaled and `false` otherwise.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="437bb-122">`AutoResetEvent` 还可与 `static` <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitAll%2A> 和方法一起使用 <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitAny%2A> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-122">`AutoResetEvent` can also be used with the `static` <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitAll%2A> and <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.WaitAny%2A> methods.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="437bb-123">从 .NET Framework 版本2.0 开始， <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> 派生自新 <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> 类。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-123">Beginning with the .NET Framework version 2.0, <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> derives from the new <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-124"><xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent>在功能上等效于 <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> 使用创建的 <xref:System.Threading.EventResetMode.AutoReset?displayProperty=nameWithType> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-124">An <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> is functionally equivalent to an <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> created with <xref:System.Threading.EventResetMode.AutoReset?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="437bb-125">与 <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> 类不同， <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> 类提供对已命名的系统同步事件的访问。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-125">Unlike the <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> class, the <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle> class provides access to named system synchronization events.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
