 <span data-ttu-id="437bb-131">从第一个线程释放线程后 <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> ，它们会等待另一个 <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> 在非终止状态下创建的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-131">After the threads are released from the first <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent>, they wait on another <xref:System.Threading.AutoResetEvent> that was created in the non-signaled state.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="437bb-132">所有三个线程都块，因此 <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A> 必须调用方法三次以释放全部。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="437bb-132">All three threads block, so the <xref:System.Threading.EventWaitHandle.Set%2A> method must be called three times to release them all.</span></span>  
  
